name: Eternal Walk
description: This is my first NFT. It's a part of something bigger. But it means something on its own too. Remember where you're going. You can look behind. Look at the sides if you want. The world is indeed a scary place. Just don't let your mind stop walking.   This was made on Adobe Illustrator and After Effects, hope you enjoy this 800x600 infinite loop. made on Adobe Illustrator and After Effects. You can see part of the process in my instagram feed (@fractal_vector)
